&nbsp;
Parliamentary Dem, according to the 6 witnesses, would be the author of two other similar episodes: one just before Christmas and the other on March 27 last. The pm will now have to decide whether to listen to the MP. After three roads would be opened: the prosecutor could decide to ask the gip to archive the procedure for insussistency of evidence, or to request the storage request for the 'particular tenuity of the fact' or, again, to close the investigation and move forward. According to AGI, in these hours the magistrates are being evaluated.&nbsp;
